data.description: MAINTENANCE FREE 2Bed/2Bath CONDO! Located within the fabulous Kings Point community. Upon entry, to your left, you will find the Kitchen with a Breakfast Bar overlooking the dining room and Great room area. Moving further into the home, you will have the two bedrooms and two bathrooms to your right. This maintenance-free 55+ golf community features 24/7 security, three clubhouses with amenities, 850-seat Veterans Theater, 6 heated swimming pools, tennis courts and pickle ball courts, fitness centers, café’s and so much more! Even has its own free transportation system, and allows access to doctors, hospitals, shopping, banking and restaurants via golf cart. Minutes away from our award winning Beaches, Airports, Fishing and Much More! Do not let this Kings Point Condo pass you by.
